# Scenario 00 — idle baseline.
#
# Detection is DISABLED via /api/detection/config PATCH (run_scenario.sh
# handles that). The worker keeps draining frames so the camera pipeline
# stays warm but burns no CUDA. This is the "everything else" baseline:
# MediaMTX + NVENC + FastAPI + push service + heartbeat.
#
# Empty env file is intentional — no detector overrides.
